<p class="paraStyle1">Admissions open for the academic session 2021-22 for classes Pre-Nursery to Grade VIII.</p>
<ul class="marLeft1">
<li  class="paraStyle1">Registration is the first step for seeking admission in BUDDHA INTERNATIONALPUBLIC SCHOOL, VPO KHURAMPUR, ASAUDHA-KHARKHODA ROAD, KHARKHODA, DISTT. SONIPAT.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">Registration forms will be available on all working days at the Administration Office from 9:00 AM to 2:00 PM.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">Incomplete registration forms will not be processed.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">Parents are advised not to fill more than one form for an applicant.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">On confirmation of grant of admission, parents shall be required to deposit the fee within stipulated time. Failing which the offer of admission shall stand cancelled and the seat will be offered to another candidate.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">The management of the school reserves all rights of admission or rejection and is not bound to give any reasons for admission or rejection of any particular candidate.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">Incomplete registration forms and forms providing incorrect information will automatically stand rejected.</li>

</ul>



<p class="paraStyle1"><span style="color:Red"><b>Caution: </b></span>The school does not accept any donation for admission. Parents should be aware of third parties collecting money on behalf of the school and making false claims of procuring admission. If the parents enter into any transaction with such parties, they will be doing so at their own risk and the school shall not be responsible for it.</p>

